Name: FEB - Brazilian Elite Force
About the game: After an alien arives in Brazil, the brazilian army created the FEB - Brazilian Elite Force, a high tech agency with only the best of the bests. Choose one of three agents: Samanta, Zolrys and Silva, and save Brazil from an alien invasion in this 2D platform/shooter game. Features: - 3 playable characters; - 5 levels, each one with a challenging Boss; - 1 level in the shmup style; - Rock/Metal original soundtrack; - Face waves of enemies in the Survival Mode.
